# Smart Hospital Management System — Full Assignment Tracker

## SECTION A: OOP (40 marks)

| Req | Description | Status | Notes |
|-----|-------------|--------|-------|
| 1 | Encapsulation (private attrs, getters/setters) | ✅ Done | All entities have private fields + getters/setters |
| 2 | Inheritance (Person → Patient/Doctor/Nurse/Receptionist) | ✅ Done | `Person` abstract, SINGLE_TABLE inheritance |
| 3 | Abstraction (PersonService, PatientService, etc.) | ✅ Done | 11 service interfaces + impls |
| 4 | Polymorphism (Person ref → Patient/Doctor/Nurse) | ✅ Done | JPA inheritance hierarchy, PersonService |
| 5 | Method Overloading (searchPatient() overloads) | ✅ Done | `PatientServiceImpl` — by id, name, email, name+phone |
| 6 | Method Overriding (displayProfile, calculateCharges, generateReport) | ✅ Done | Entities override inherited methods |
| 7 | Composition (Patient has MedicalRecord, EmergencyContact, Address) | ✅ Done | CascadeType.ALL, owned entities |
| 8 | Aggregation (Department has many Doctors) | ✅ Done | Department → @OneToMany Doctor |
| 9 | Association (Patients consult Doctors) | ✅ Done | Entity relationships established |
| 10 | Constructors (default, parameterized, copy) | ⚠️ Partial | Copy constructor on User, AuditLog only — add to other entities |

