## SECTION F: Business Rules (20 marks)

| Rule | Status | Notes |
|------|--------|-------|
| 1. National ID unique | ✅ Done | `@Column(unique = true)` on `Patient.nationalId` |
| 2. Patient email unique | ✅ Done | `@Column(unique = true)` on `Person.email` |
| 3. Doctor: no overlapping appointments | ✅ Done | JPQL overlap check in `AppointmentServiceImpl` |
| 4. Patient: no double-booking | ✅ Done | JPQL count check in `AppointmentServiceImpl` |
| 5. Emergency patients priority | ❌ Missing | `SECTION-F.md` describes it but no `PriorityQueue<Patient>` in production code |
| 6. Bills after consultation completed | ✅ Done | Status check in `BillingServiceImpl.generateInvoice()` |
| 7. Prescriptions after diagnosis | ✅ Done | Appointment status check in `PrescriptionServiceImpl` |
| 8. Lab tests require doctor's request | ✅ Done | Field validation in `LaboratoryTestServiceImpl` |
| 9. Only admins may delete | ✅ Done | `SecurityConfig` guards `DELETE /**` + `@PreAuthorize` on all `@DeleteMapping` |
| 10. Soft delete | ✅ Done | `@SQLDelete` + `@SQLRestriction` on `Person` |

